trans-unit.source: Specifies the possible alignments with which the items of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> can be displayed.
trans-unit.target: 指定可能的對齊方式與其的項目<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>可以顯示。

trans-unit.source: You control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> layout by choosing one of the members of ToolStripLayoutStyle with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutStyle%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 您可以控制<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>版面配置選擇其中一個 ToolStripLayoutStyle 與成員<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutStyle%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutStyle%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Stack Layouts Stacking is the arranging of items beside each other at both ends of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.
trans-unit.target: 堆疊配置堆疊是彼此旁邊<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>兩端的項目排列

trans-unit.source: The following list describes the stack layouts.
trans-unit.target: 下列清單描述堆疊配置。

trans-unit.source: - StackWithOverflow is the default.
trans-unit.target: -預設值為 StackWithOverflow。

trans-unit.source: This setting causes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> to alter its layout automatically in accordance with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Orientation%2A> property to handle dragging and docking scenarios.
trans-unit.target: 這項設定會導致<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>改變它自動在按照所使用的版面配置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Orientation%2A>屬性來處理拖曳和停駐的案例。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Orientation%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: - VerticalStackWithOverflow renders the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> items beside each other vertically.
trans-unit.target: -VerticalStackWithOverflow 呈現<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>旁邊彼此垂直項目。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: - HorizontalStackWithOverflow renders the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> items beside each other horizontally.
trans-unit.target: -HorizontalStackWithOverflow 呈現<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>旁邊彼此水平項目。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Other Features of Stack Layouts <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Alignment%2A> determines the end of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> to which the item is aligned.
trans-unit.target: 其他功能的堆疊配置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Alignment%2A>決定結尾<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>以項目對齊。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Alignment%2A>

trans-unit.source: When items do not fit within the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, an overflow button automatically appears.
trans-unit.target: 當項目無法納入<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>，溢位按鈕就會自動出現。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A> property setting determines whether an item appears in the overflow area always, as needed, or never.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A>屬性設定會決定項目是否要出現在溢位區域一律，如有需要或永遠不會。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A>

trans-unit.source: In the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutCompleted> event, you can inspect the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Placement%2A> property to determine whether an item was placed on the main <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, the overflow <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>, or if it is not currently showing at all.
trans-unit.target: 在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutCompleted>事件，您可以檢查<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Placement%2A>屬性來判斷項目是否已放在主要<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>，溢位<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>，或如果它目前未顯示根本。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Placement%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.LayoutCompleted>

trans-unit.source: The typical reasons why an item is not displayed are that the item did not fit on the main <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> and its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A> property was set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemOverflow>.
trans-unit.target: 項目不會顯示原因的常見原因是，不適用項目上的主要<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>和其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A>屬性已設定為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemOverflow>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemOverflow> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem.Overflow%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: Make a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> movable by putting it in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel> and setting its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A> to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripGripStyle>.
trans-unit.target: 請<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>將放入它<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel>，並設定其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A>至<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripGripStyle>。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripGripStyle></xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.GripStyle%2A></xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripPanel>可移動</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>
